Paper: hep-th/0010037

Date: 2000-10-06

Title: Statistics of the Composite System

Authors: Hitoshi Ito

Comments: 4pages

The space-like asymptotic limit of the bilocal composite field of the stateconsisting of a nucleus and an electron is studied. It is shown that theresulting local field of an atom satisfies the proper commutation relations inthe sub-Fock-space of the atom.